Question:
    Cruise is paid for can we still buy travel insurance?    
Mary, 
 
03/18/2017





Answer:  You can purchase most policies up until the day before departure, however; you may not be eligible for some time sensitive benefits if you do not purchase within 10-30 days of the initial trip deposit/payment.  Some time sensitive benefits are, but not limited to: Pre-Existing Condition Waiver, Financial Default, Terrorism, Cancel For Any Reason and Cancel For Work Reasons.    
    
MattG, 
Customer Care insureMyTrip 

03/21/2017

    
