now you're covered in case your vacation is interrupted or delayed by a covered circumstance out of your control. Help is just a phone call away, 24 hours a day. Avoid Emergency Medical Expenses- If you come down with malaria on a mission trip, or you're in a car crash in Bangkok, you'll swiftly discover that medical costs in other countries can be astronomical. A covered injury or illness may require emergency medical transportation to the nearest qualified medical facility, potentially costing $100,000 or more. Travel insurance from Allianz Global Assistance is designed to reimburse your covered emergency healthcare expenses, wherever you are.                Allianz User Reviews             The next time you travel, make sure you're protected with Travel Insurance from Allianz Global Assistance. With it, you can receive protection for:  Trip Cancellation/Trip Interruption Emergency Medical & Dental Care Emergency Medical Transportation Baggage Loss/Damage 24-Hour Concierge Service                               Allianz Global Assistance USA Allianz Global Assistance USA (AGA Service Company) is a leading consumer specialty insurance and assistance company. We insure 21 million customers annually and are best known for our Allianz Travel Insurance plans. In addition to travel insurance, Allianz Global Assistance USA offers tuition insurance, event ticket protection, registration protection for endurance events and unique travel assistance services such as international medical assistance and concierge services. The company also serves as an outsource provider for in-bound call center services and claims administration for health insurers, property and casualty insurers, and credit card companies.              Terms, conditions, and exclusions apply. Please see the Certificate of Insurance/Policy, during the check-out process, for full details.       *CDI coverage, except when purchased as a separate policy, is not available to TX residents. Insurance coverage is und