  Low cost and affordable price.  Per incident coverage.  Good for basic medical coverage.  Pre-existing Condition rider coverage for heart related existing conditions.  Renewable.  Cancelable and refundable. (Full refund before start date, prorated refund if there is no claim- $25 applicable cancellation fee)      What's Not Good About Visitors Care  Coverage and benefits may not be adequate. Plan pays fixed, pre-defined rate for each service. Maximum 12 months of coverage. Only $10,000 coverage limit for travelers over 80 years of age. Precertification required for certain medical treatments to avoid 50% reduction in benefits.       Visitors Care Insurance Feedback, Reviews and Ratings  Visit any doctor or hospital. Visitors Care has good feedback and Reviews from customers. Licensed and regulated by Dept. of insurance in United States. All claims are handled in USA.    How It Works After the deductible plan pays:  As per the pre defined schedule of benefits.  See complete Details -  How Visitors Care insurance plan works?    Plan Info Visitors Care Insurance Brochure  Visitors Care Insurance Providers Directory Visitors Care Insurance FAQsVisitors Care Online Renewal    Visitors Care Insurance Plan Benefit Details Visitors Care Insurance Claims Forms  Description of Coverage   Cancellation Process      Visitors Care Visitor Insurance Experiences Visitors Care offer excellent benefits at a very affordable price, and is among one the popular choice of visitors. You can read and post your customers experiences about Visitors Care visitor insurance.   Manage your Visitors Care Insurance Policy Online: Renewal, Extension, Visa Letter more  Patriot Insurance policy can be managed online . If you are policy holder you can logon to Patriot insurance online myIMG to renew, extend, download ID card, making any correction, Visa letter, Find providers etc. You will need the Policy ID and Date of birth of the insurance person to access Patriot america insurance client Zone.  