Barney Harford Overview
                    

Barney Harford has been associated with five companies, according to public records. The companies were formed over a thirteen year period with the most recent being incorporated nine years ago in January of 2008. Zero of the companies are still active while the remaining five are now listed as inactive. 
                    
                






