Question:
    Cruise booked but need insurance as I am flying to the cruise liner from Bulgaria,British Passport but now live in Bulgaria
Can I get insurance that covers me for flight and cruise    
Alan, 
 
06/15/2017





Answer:  Yes, as long as your travel arrangements are prepaid and non-refundable, you can insure them with any one of our comprehensive plans.    
    
