    What country do I put if I am traveling to multiple countries while on vacation to be covered for medical insurance for the entire trip?    
Sami, 
 
06/05/2017





Answer:  Please list the first destination or the destination where you are spending the most of your time in.    
    
MattG, 
Customer Care insureMyTrip 

