t a refund, provided you haven’t started your trip or initiated a claim.  Premiums are non-refundable after this period.                    Why Buy Travel Insurance For Your Cruise? Allianz Global Assistance, a world leader in travel insurance and assistance services, can offer many reasons why millions of travelers protect themselves and their families with travel insurance. They're the people we help every year through unanticipated travel delays, missed cruise embarkations and medical emergencies in foreign countries.  Last Minute Cancellation- You've been planning your dream cruise for a year - and then you get sick the day before departure. Allianz Global Assistance's cruise travel insurance can insure for covered illness, injury and even losing your job, and can ensure you get back your nonrefundable costs. On-Board Medical Emergency- Ships' doctors aren't equipped to handle serious medical crises. If you suffer a serious covered health crisis while cruising, evacuation coverage can pay to transport you to the nearest appropriate medical facility. Missed Connection- If your flight gets delayed, the ship won't wait. Allianz Global Assistance can help you make new travel arrangements to catch up with your cruise ship and may reimburse you for those additional expenses. (You must, however, make a reasonable effort to minimize travel costs.) Trip Interruption- If you have to cut your cruise short for a covered reason, travel insurance may reimburse you for the part of the cruise you miss as well as your costs to return home early.                Allianz User Reviews             The next time you travel, make sure you're protected with Travel Insurance from Allianz Global Assistance. With it, you can receive protection for:  Trip Cancellation/Trip Interruption Emergency Medical & Dental Care Emergency Medical Transportation Baggage Loss/Damage 24-Hour Concierge Service                               Allianz Global Assistance USA Allianz Global Assistance USA (AGA Se